\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
noindent
\end_layout

\end_inset

 We will optimize the set of variational parameters 
\begin_inset Formula $\{v_{i\mathbf{k}}\}$
\end_inset

 in order to minimize 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{{\rm B}}$
\end_inset

 (i.e.
 to make it as close to the true free energy 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 as possible).
 Neglecting the higher order terms and using 
