\ensuremath{{\rm \text{Tr}}}\left(e^{-\beta\overline{H_{\bar{S}}}\left(t\right)}\right) & ={\rm exp}\left(-\frac{\varepsilon\left(t\right)\beta}{2}\right){\rm exp}\left(\frac{\eta\left(t\right)\beta}{2}\right)+{\rm exp}\left(-\frac{\varepsilon\left(t\right)\beta}{2}\right){\rm exp}\left(-\frac{\eta\left(t\right)\beta}{2}\right)\\
