 to calculate 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{{\rm \partial}{\rm {\rm \text{Tr}}}\left(e^{-\beta\overline{H_{\bar{S}}}\left(t\right)}\right)}{\partial\Re\left(v_{i\mathbf{k}}\right)}$
\end_inset

